        "Check the logs of the 'pcf' container for errors related to MongoDB connectivity.",
        "Restart the 'mongo' container and observe if the 'pcscf_sip_error_ratio' metric returns to its healthy baseline of 0.",
        "Query the PCF's status endpoint directly to confirm it is in a failed state."
      ],
      "specificity": "specific"
    },
    {
      "id": "h2",
      "statement": "A network partition or a failure of the Rx interface is preventing the P-CSCF from communicating with the PCF. This communication breakdown is causing QoS authorization to fail, resulting in the rejection of SIP INVITEs.",
